{"tid":532283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連台灣人都話國語係北京胡語！！！","createTime":"2018-01-17T16:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T02:34:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4ea00e6de019deec83ee02244e63f957eb4f07","tid":532283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://taiwanwe.org/discuss01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaiwanwe.org%2Fdiscuss01.htm&d=ylOtWB8qs9gat1RKTDBNC54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=14465e68\" target=\"_blank\">http://taiwanwe.org/discuss01.htm</a><br />\n漢人未來台灣之前，整個台灣平地都是平埔族的天下，在漢人入侵的強勢文化與統治下，平埔族的語言、文化、人種全部消失無蹤。北京語（<span style=\"color: red;\">國語，應該稱為北京胡語較適合</span>）並非純漢語，在五胡亂華及元宋，胡族入侵的強大政治力量下，原來北方官話的漢語與胡語混合，形成入聲消失，簡化成四聲的變種語言──北京胡語。政治、教育及傳播媒體消滅台語的力量，在國民黨的掌控下，實在太恐怖了，台灣各族群的語言與文化，在國民黨外來政權的殖民地心態統治下，如不大力挽救，必然走上平埔族滅亡的命運。"},{"pid":"141b5aca0707fef6d7b27b00a1fabffe868143ab","tid":532283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.innshops.com/goods.php?id=567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.innshops.com%2Fgoods.php%3Fid%3D567&d=ylOtWB8qs9gat1RKTDBNC54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=27233aea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.innshops.com/goods.php?id=567</a>"},{"pid":"d3a85eb058d8071f75af3408b0e5a73424de7063","tid":532283,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:42:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/Longood-Home-Furniture/s/H0786001/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E9%9B%9C%E8%B2%A8/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E9%9B%9C%E8%B2%A8/%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%AE%A2%E5%BB%B3/%E7%B5%84%E5%90%88%E6%AB%83-%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E6%AB%83/12%E7%B1%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%BC%8F%E8%B6%9F%E9%96%80%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E6%AB%83%E6%AB%BB%E6%A1%83%E9%85%8D%E7%99%BD%E8%89%B2/p/H0786001_S_LGT24SLW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktvmall.com%2Fhktv%2Fzh%2Fmain%2FLong